    /// \brief Indicates the unique ID of a Path within the RoutePlan that is being
    /// referenced. This element is used if a specific Path is being referenced,
    /// excluding others. If specified, all Segments of the Path are being
    /// referenced except when further constrained by the sibling SegmentID. If
    /// this element and the sibling SegmentID are not specified, then all Paths
    /// and Segments of the RoutePlan are included in the reference.
