/// collection, track, or search as part of an XX Activity. If the XX Subsystem
/// cannot point itself, then the TurretSlaved Type is used. If the system
/// wants to allow the subsystem to control its own LOS then the
/// ActivitySlavedID is used. FixedPointing is used to point to a predetermined
/// location defined by its Enum values.
